title: Tape808 Samples by GoldBaby
description:
They say: "Not another 808 sample! Well actually it isn&#039;t... this is 407 samples taken from two 808&#039;s recorded into an Ampex 351 1/2" valve 2 track tape machine! That&#039;s not all... We also put the 808&#039;s through other vintage gear. Plus we recorded the 808&#039;s naked into a Metric Halo ULN-2 firewire audio card. Then we chose the best samples.

All 24 bit, and all phat analog goodness!

If you can&#039;t get a hold of a real 808 then this is as close as you can get in samples... Maybe even better than the having the real thing!"

I say: This samples are cool, if you like them and use them, consider buying something from Goldbaby.co.nz to show your support!
